quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,49,"(Aey Muhammad), kehdo ke “ logon, main to tumhare liye sirf woh shaks hoon jo (bura waqt aane se pehle) saaf saaf khabardar karne wala ho"
  22,50,Phir jo iman layenge aur neik amal karenge unke liye magfirat hai aur izzat ki rozi
  22,51,Aur jo hamari aayat ko neecha dikhane ki koshish karenge woh dozakh ke yaar hain
  22,52,"Aur (aey Muhammad) tumse pehle humne na koi Rasool aisa bheja hai na Nabi (jiske saath yeh maamla na pesh aaya ho ke) jab usne tamanna ki, shaytan uski tamanna mein khalal andaz ho gaya. Is tarah jo kuch bhi shaytan khalal andaziyan karta hai Allah unko mita deta hai aur apni aayat ko pukhta (confirm) kardeta hai. Allah aleem hai aur hakeem"
  22,53,"(Woh is liye aisa honay deta hai) taa-ke shaytan ki daali hui kharabi ko fitna bana de un logon ke liye jinke dilon ko [nifaq ka (hypocrisy)] rog laga hua hai aur jinke dil khotay hain. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh zalim log inaad (enmity) mein bahut door nikal gaye hain"
  22,54,Aur ilam se behramand log jaan lein ke yeh haqq hai tere Rubb ki taraf se aur woh ispar iman le aayein aur unke dil iske aagey jhuk jaayein. Yaqeenan Allah iman laney walon ko hamesha seedha raasta dikha deta hai
  22,55,"Inkar karne waley to iski taraf se shakk hi mein padey rahenge yaha tak ke ya to unpar qayamat ki ghadi achanak aa jaye, ya ek manhoos din ka azaab nazil ho jaye"
  22,56,Us roz baadshahi Allah ki hogi aur woh unke darmiyan faisla kardega. Jo iman rakhne waley aur amal e saleh karne waley hongey woh niyamat bhari jannaton mein jayenge
  22,57,Aur jinhon ne kufr kiya hoga aur hamari aayat ko jhutlaya hoga unke liye ruswakun azaab hoga